driver.name: GcodeDriver
driver.detected-firmware: FIRMWARE_NAME:Smoothieware, FIRMWARE_URL:http%3A//smoothieware.org, X-SOURCE_CODE_URL:https%3A//github.com/c-riegel/Smoothieware-CHMT, FIRMWARE_VERSION:chmt-fed207a1, X-FIRMWARE_BUILD_DATE:Feb 21 2022 11:42:46, X-SYSTEM_CLOCK:168MHz, X-AXES:7, X-PAXES:7, X-GRBL_MODE:0, X-SERIAL_FLOW:NONE, X-CNC:0, X-MSD:1

command.text: M82 ; Set absolute mode for extruder
G92.1 ; remove any previously applied offsets
G0 Z40 ; move Z-axis into free space to allow good homing
G28 Z ; home Z first and apply an offset to compensator for unbalanced z homing position
G92 Z2.4 ; apply Z offset to compensator for unbalanced z homing position
G28 X Y ; home X and Y axes
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
{True:M800 ; on, open solenoid valve, RED led ON on soleonid }
{False:M801 ; off, close solenoid valve, RED led OFF on soleonid }
{True:M804 ; on, open solenoid valve, RED led ON on soleonid }
{False:M805 ; off, close solenoid valve, RED led OFF on soleonid }
{True: G4 P10} ; wait a little bit until the pin is down
{False: G4 P100} ; wait a little bit until the pin is up (avoid false interlock errors)
G92 C0 G0 C6 ; Set absolute position to 0, Move 6mm
M80{True:8}{False:9} ; VAC M808 on / M809 off
M81{True:2}{False:3} ; BLOW M812 on / M813 off
M81{True:0}{False:1} ; UPLED M810 on / M811 off
M81{True:4}{False:5} ; DOWNLED M814 on / M815 off
M81{True:8}{False:9} ; CAMSW M818 on / M819 off
M81{True:2S50}{False:3} ; BLOW M812 on / M813 off
M81{True:2}{False:3} ; BLOW M812 on / M813 off
M81{True:2}{False:3} ; BLOW M812 on / M813 off
M80{True:8}{False:9}; VAC M808 on / M809 off
{True:G92 C0 G0 C6} ; Set absolute position to 0, Move 6mm
{True:M802 ; on, open solenoid valve, RED led ON on soleonid }
{False:M803 ; off, close solenoid valve, RED led OFF on soleonid }
M808 S{IntegerValue} ; set VAC to given power [%]
; FIXME: this uses seek motion with is not configured
{False:G92 C0 G0 C6} ; Set absolute position to 0, Move 6mm when switched off
; not used, blower is operated as PWM using ACTUATOR_DOUBLE
;{True: M808 S50} ; set VAC to given power [%]
; FIXME: this uses seek motion with is not configured
{False:G92 C0 G0 C14} ; Set absolute position to 0, Move 14mm when switched off
M82{True:2 S10}{False:1} ; DOWNLED M822 on / M823 off
M822 S{DoubleValue} ; DOWNLED M822 on / M823 off
